lightfield (1.0.7.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * New: "Build platform offset" slider on Advanced tab. Defaults to 300 µm, range 0-1000 µm in steps of 25 µm.
  * Changed: Scrollbar thumbs ought to be easier to hit now.
  * Fixed: 'Copy files to USB' should work now.
  * Fixed: The amount indicated by the 'Dispense print solution' step should always be correct now.

 -- LightField packager <lightfield-packager@volumetricbio.com>  Mon, 19 Aug 2019 10:30:03 -0700

lightfield (1.0.6.3) stable; urgency=medium

  * New: Upon inserting a USB stick, the "Update software" button is disabled. If valid updates are found, the button is re-enabled.
  * Bug fix: The Prepare tab will now automatically advance to the Print tab if the printer is prepared and the model has been sliced.

