lightfield (1.0.5) stable; urgency=medium

  * New: "Copy logs to USB" button on System tab.
  * Changed: The "Show USB stick"/"Show Library" button on the File tab has been enlarged to make it easier to hit.
  * Changed: The "Projector power level" sliders on the Print and Advanced tabs are now linked together: changing one will change the other.
  * Changed: The "Exposure time" slider now has a range of 30 s, and is adjustable in steps of 0.25 s.
  * Changed: Make the description text box on the software update selector wider.
  * Fixed: The same update could appear in the update selector more than once.

 -- LightField packager <lightfield-packager@volumetricbio.com>  Wed, 31 Jul 2019 14:38:37 -0700

